data.description: ** Price Reduction**Gorgeous home located in the Belle Rose addition of Legacy Subdivision in North Bossier. 4 Bedroom 2 Bath with approximately 2,100 square feet. Large open kitchen with eat in area overlooking the large living room with hardwood floors. Fenced backyard with no rear neighbors. Tankless Water Heater. The neighborhood features a community pool, playground, pavilion, walking trails, and ponds. You can walk to Legacy Elementary and bus service to Benton Middle and Benton High School. Easy access to Benton, North Bossier and Barksdale Air Force Base.  Seller will consider a VA Assumption to qualified active military or veterans.
